                     <join result="defendantPunishment" targOrder="Y" targets="t18041205-9-defend126 t18041205-9-punish52"></join>
               Confined six months in the House of Correction
            </rs>, and <rs id="t18041205-9-punish53" type="punishmentDescription">
                     <interp inst="t18041205-9-punish53" type="punishmentCategory" value="miscPunish"></interp>
                     <interp inst="t18041205-9-punish53" type="punishmentSubcategory" value="fine"></interp>
                     <join result="defendantPunishment" targOrder="Y" targets="t18041205-9-defend126 t18041205-9-punish53"></join>
               fined 1 s.
            </rs>
               </p>
               <p>Finch, <rs id="t18041205-9-verdict54" type="verdictDescription">
                     <interp inst="t18041205-9-verdict54" type="verdictCategory" value="guilty"></interp>
               GUILTY
            </rs>, aged 71.</p>
               <p>
                  <rs id="t18041205-9-punish55" type="punishmentDescription">
